# SPI Display Pin Configuration:
# - MOSI (Data): GPIO 10 (Pin 19) - Hardware SPI
# - SCLK (Clock): GPIO 11 (Pin 23) - Hardware SPI  
# - CS (Chip Select): GPIO 8 (Pin 24) - Hardware SPI, or custom pin via cs_pin
# - DC (Data/Command): GPIO 24 (Pin 18) - Configurable via dc_pin
# - RST (Reset): GPIO 25 (Pin 22) - Configurable via reset_pin
# - VCC: 3.3V or 5V (Pin 1 or Pin 2)
# - GND: Ground (Pin 6, 9, 14, 20, 25, 30, 34, or 39)
#
# Display Type Options:
# - type: SSD1306 (most common) or SH1106 (alternative driver)
# - baudrate: SPI speed in Hz (try lower values if text is garbled)
# - external_vcc: true/false (depends on display power configuration)
